   * Subject: Glass
   * Date: Wed, 13 Feb 91 16:05:09 EST [1]
   * From: spworley@ATHENA.MIT.EDU

   Air             1.02
   Ice             1.309
   Alchohol        1.329
   Water           1.333
   Glass           1.50
   Quartz & salt   1.644
   Diamond         2.417

